## Sys Restaurante

#### Compile & Build

###### 1. Linux (**BASH**)

```$bash
$ find src/ -type f -name *.java > out/dev/class
```

```
$ find src/ -type f -name *.fxml -exec cp {} out/dev/bin/sysRestaurante/gui \;
```

```$bash
$ javac --module-path $PATH_TO_FX --add-modules=javafx.controls,javafx.fxml @out/dev/class -d out/dev/bin
```

```$bash
$ java -cp .:$SQLITE:out/dev/bin --module-path $PATH_TO_FX --add-modules=javafx.controls,javafx.fxml sysRestaurante.gui.MainGUI
```

